Source: The Economist (2023); WHO COVID-19 Dashboard
Note: For some countries, all-cause deaths and COVID-19 deaths use different date schemes, in which one refers to when the death occurred and
the other to when it was reported. This difference could produce an artificial lag between the two time series.
